Description:
 ctk-3-examples - example files for CTK 3
 ctk-update-icon-cache - icon theme caching utility
 gir1.2-ctk-3.0 - CTK graphical user interface library -- gir bindings
 libcail-3-0 - GNOME Accessibility Implementation Library -- shared libraries
 libcail-3-dev - GNOME Accessibility Implementation Library -- development files
 libcail-3-doc - documentation files of the Cail library
 libctk-3-0 - CTK graphical user interface library
 libctk-3-0-udeb - CTK graphical user interface library - minimal runtime (udeb)
 libctk-3-bin - programs for the CTK graphical user interface library
 libctk-3-common - common files for the CTK graphical user interface library
 libctk-3-dev - development files for the CTK library
 libctk-3-doc - documentation for the CTK graphical user interface library
Changes:
 ctk+3.0 (3.26.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium
 .
   * control:
     - Use debhelper compat level 13
     - remove librsvg2-common
   * tests,control: remove librsvg2-common
   * port from GdkPixbuf to CdkPixbuf
   * New upstream release
